      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Is JavaCoder free to use?</h4>
          <p>Yes, it’s 100% free for students and teachers. Admin approval required for teacher access.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">What makes JavaCoder different?</h4>
          <p>It's more than a classroom—real-time rating, automated transfer system, and AI-generated quizzes make it powerful.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Can I track student performance?</h4>
          <p>Yes! Teachers and admins can track quiz scores, assignment submissions, and ratings.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

