        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-600 mb-3">📖 Quality Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Delivering real-world coding knowledge and interactive lessons for every student—no matter their location or background.</p>
